[H[2J[3J
-------------
Lets configure the on-chain delay / cooling period
for spending with your private-key from your Vault!

This will give you time to react and initiate recovery
when your private-key or wallet backup (seed phrase) is stolen
and is used to unlock your Vault.
-------------
Enter delay in blocks [Default: 1000]: Setting Option 1 (User Private-Key Only) Delay to 1000
Encoded bytes (hex): e803
[H[2J[3J
-------------
Now, lets configure the on-chain delay / cooling period
for spending with the Sentinel private-key from your Vault!

This is the delay your Sentinel has to wait before he can
transfer/recover from your Vault in case your private-key
is lost or for managing your inheritance.

PS: This is typically much longer than the previously set delay
and will give you time to react and override any spend attempt
by rogue Sentinels with just your private-key eliminating
counter-party risk from the Hybrid Custody System.
